\begin_layout Standard
[Main Conclusion] The model attempts to find the conditions in an environment
 of uncertainty that justifies status consumption ...
 .
 The model interprets the relevance of local reference points as the personal
 equilibirum of consumers.
 This takes an approach that is more general and of more descriptive relevance
 than many of the models we've explored.
 As the roots of subjective inference lie in exchangeability 
