 As the roots of uncertainty lie in exchangeability, the very presence of
 social hierarchy can be interpreted as individuals associating a higher
 subjective probability with a certain characteristics 
\begin_inset Formula $\rho$
\end_inset

 - by considering individuals with the same characteristics 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

exchangeable
\begin_inset Quotes erd
